  06 Mar 2009; Christian Faulhammer <fauli@gentoo.org>
  python-mode-5.1.0.ebuild:
  introduce src_unpack() in a proper way, so the package actually installs

  06 Mar 2009; Christian Faulhammer <fauli@gentoo.org>
  files/61python-mode-gentoo.el, python-mode-5.1.0.ebuild:
  import KEYWORDS from tree and remove doctest-mode from SITEFILE

  08 Feb 2009; Christian Faulhammer <fauli@gentoo.org>
  python-mode-5.1.0.ebuild:
  use EAPI=2 for SRC_URI redirection, so we have a versioned DISTFILE on the
  local disk, this still saves us the src_unpack() function without the
  hassle of self-created distfile

  07 Feb 2009; Ulrich Mueller <ulm@gentoo.org> python-mode-5.1.0.ebuild:
  Remove unused flag from IUSE. Use versioned distfile.

*python-mode-5.1.0 (07 Feb 2009)

  07 Feb 2009; Christian Faulhammer <fauli@gentoo.org>
  +files/61python-mode-gentoo.el, +metadata.xml, +python-mode-5.1.0.ebuild:
  make a version bump as split-out of app-emacs/python-mode in the official
  tree

